{"tid":722594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（估國家）19歲男子和女友在公園約會 遭人拿刀砍殺","createTime":"2018-06-29T15:50:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T10:45:02.000Z","uid":160807,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fcb9bce79e24d265337ac879d5a2cb818216fece","tid":722594,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T15:50:15.000Z","msg":"新北市永和凌晨發生情侶約會，男生竟被人拿刀砍殺的事件。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/NF.ehHLwB43.Xnf8Nl.G_Q--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/news_tvbs_com_tw_938/f683bf978ff2ca01a191849519cf9e07\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FNF.ehHLwB43.Xnf8Nl.G_Q--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fnews_tvbs_com_tw_938%2Ff683bf978ff2ca01a191849519cf9e07&h=8ac21e99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今天凌晨0時可以看到警方和鑑識人員不斷在公園草叢外搜尋，甚至拿出金屬偵測器，想找找看有沒有留下刀械，因為有人在這兒被人砍殺。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/EijxezEFKN11iqd6yBFWww--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/news_tvbs_com_tw_938/7534c520fb68d520ccaf96950bdccbd0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FEijxezEFKN11iqd6yBFWww--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fnews_tvbs_com_tw_938%2F7534c520fb68d520ccaf96950bdccbd0&h=f61cd494&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新北市永和仁愛公園現場，除了遺留的安全帽，周遭都是血跡。凌晨12點多，19歲何姓男子和女朋友在這裡約會到一半，突然一輛車停在他們旁邊，接著衝下來3名惡煞，直接拿刀朝他狂砍，女朋友哭著報案，緊急將傷者送醫，朋友和父母接到消息也連忙趕往醫院。<br />\n<br />\n何姓男子身上，包括肩膀、背部和腰部多處刀傷，其中3刀較為嚴重，一度情況危急。開刀後目前暫時沒有生命危險。而目擊一切的女友也被帶往警局要來瞭解始末並且找出動手惡煞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/19%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E5%92%8C%E5%A5%B3%E5%8F%8B%E5%9C%A8%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%E7%B4%84%E6%9C%83-%E9%81%AD%E4%BA%BA%E6%8B%BF%E5%88%80%E7%A0%8D%E6%AE%BA-011354179.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F19%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%2592%258C%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%258F%258B%25E5%259C%25A8%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%259C%2592%25E7%25B4%2584%25E6%259C%2583-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%258B%25BF%25E5%2588%2580%25E7%25A0%258D%25E6%25AE%25BA-011354179.html&d=sQfMvwtWSOMjRR2zQj9a08n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=b03f6b91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/19%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E5%92%8C%E5%A5%B3%E5%8F%8B%E5%9C%A8%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%E7%B4%84%E6%9C%83-%E9%81%AD%E4%BA%BA%E6%8B%BF%E5%88%80%E7%A0%8D%E6%AE%BA-011354179.html</a>"},{"pid":"bd19fbcb88d18f7bf1e2103d86c99668dcb7de6f","tid":722594,"uid":83341,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T15:51:00.000Z","msg":"以為係印度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adc9e2b9e6e019372b4b4dc7dd62dd4668608282","tid":722594,"uid":179547,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T15:58:04.000Z","msg":"砍殺以為死咗，標題可唔可以再誤導啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d526508de4b703cc32dfa6722ab3e639fea051b","tid":722594,"uid":67500,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T16:07:20.000Z","msg":"騎馬與砍殺"},{"pid":"d8053fe0067b948aea635b739b8856f24e8ef655","tid":722594,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adc9e2b9e6e019372b4b4dc7dd62dd4668608282","tid":722594,"uid":179547,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T15:58:04.000Z","msg":"砍殺以為死咗，標題可唔可以再誤導啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T17:49:46.000Z","msg":"台灣記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0407c25293857cc5942215e504a63fc126dc96d5","tid":722594,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T10:45:02.000Z","msg":"爭女"}]}